data.description: Adorable house with three very nice sized bedrooms and big kitchen and living area! Move in ready! Nice large lot and convenient to the freeway. Very nice screened porch with new screens. House has a large  basement area with a fireplace that can be easily converted into a man cave, hangout spot or a she shed. Hardwood flooring in most of the house. This house has a lot of awesome potential. Come and make it yours.
